<h2>Overview</h2>

<p>I don't write travel reviews often — when I do, it's because a place genuinely earned it. Krabi Garuda is one of those places. I booked this trip through <a href="https://krabigaruda.com" rel="noopener noreferrer">krabigaruda.com</a> and from the moment the reservation confirmed to the moment my transfer pulled away, the experience was consistently excellent. I'm full-time nomad — no home base, just a carry-on and a long list of places worth returning to. Krabi Garuda made that list.</p>

